scsi first has a scsi host bus adapter:
	this one used as a controller to control all type of buses it supports:
	every kind of bus can attach a limited number of devices
	then device has lun(logical unit number)
layer:
	hba(scsi host)=>channel(bus)=>device(id)=>lun(lun)
initiator:
	this is the scsi host, the one invoking requests
